{
  "page": "War for the White Cloaks",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>War for the White Cloaks</b> is the <a href=\"/index.php/Maesters\" title=\"Maesters\">maesters</a>' name for <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney\" title=\"Tourney\">tourney</a> melees held during the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Wedding\" title=\"Golden Wedding\">Golden Wedding</a> of Queen Regent <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa Velaryon</a> to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Baratheon\" title=\"Rogar Baratheon\">Rogar Baratheon</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/49_AC\" title=\"49 AC\">49&#160;AC</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Victors\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Victors</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=War_for_the_White_Cloaks&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Because there were five vacancies in the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> after young king <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">Jaehaerys I Targaryen</a> succeeded his uncle <a href=\"/index.php/Maegor_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Maegor I Targaryen\">Maegor I Targaryen</a> on the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Throne\" title=\"Iron Throne\">Iron Throne</a>, Queen Regent <a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa Velaryon</a> suggested that her son award white cloaks to champions of the tourney which would follow her <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Wedding\" title=\"Golden Wedding\">Golden Wedding</a> to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Rogar_Baratheon\" title=\"Rogar Baratheon\">Rogar Baratheon</a>. Jaehaerys decided that the contenders would fight on foot instead of jousting, as foes seldom strike a king from <a href=\"/index.php/Horse\" title=\"Horse\">horseback</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The tourney lasted seven days, with the jousting tilts overshadowed by wild melees and bloody duels. Hundreds of <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> competed with <a href=\"/index.php/Armament\" title=\"Armament\">axe</a>, spear, and sword for the honor of serving in the Kingsguard. Several colorful competitors became favorites of the <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a>, such as Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Willam_Stafford\" title=\"Willam Stafford\">Willam Stafford</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Tom_the_Strummer\" title=\"Tom the Strummer\">Tom the Strummer</a>, and a <a href=\"/index.php/Mystery_knight\" title=\"Mystery knight\">mystery knight</a> revealed to be <a href=\"/index.php/Jonquil_Darke\" title=\"Jonquil Darke\">Jonquil Darke</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Victors\">Victors</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=War_for_the_White_Cloaks&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Victors\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The five champions named to the Kingsguard were:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Lorence_Roxton\" title=\"Lorence Roxton\">Lorence Roxton</a>, a noble of the <a href=\"/index.php/Reach\" title=\"Reach\">Reach</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Victor_the_Valiant\" title=\"Victor the Valiant\">Victor the Valiant</a>, a sworn sword of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/House_Royce\" title=\"House Royce\">Royce</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Runestone\" title=\"Runestone\">Runestone</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Willam_the_Wasp\" title=\"Willam the Wasp\">Willam the Wasp</a>, a sworn sword of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Myles_Smallwood\" title=\"Myles Smallwood\">Myles Smallwood</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Acorn_Hall\" title=\"Acorn Hall\">Acorn Hall</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Pate_the_Woodcock\" title=\"Pate the Woodcock\">Pate the Woodcock</a>, a youth knighted by Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Doggett\" title=\"Joffrey Doggett\">Joffrey Doggett</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Samgood_of_Sour_Hill\" title=\"Samgood of Sour Hill\">Samgood of Sour Hill</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Hedge_knight\" title=\"Hedge knight\">hedge knight</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes\">Quotes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=War_for_the_White_Cloaks&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>I want the <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knights</a> protecting <a href=\"/index.php/Jaehaerys_I_Targaryen\" title=\"Jaehaerys I Targaryen\">my son</a> to be the finest to be found anywhere in <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a>, true honest men whose loyalty and courage is unquestioned. Let them win their <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">cloaks</a> with deeds of arms, whilst all the <a href=\"/index.php/Seven_Kingdoms\" title=\"Seven Kingdoms\">realm</a> looks on.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Alyssa_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyssa Velaryon\">Alyssa Velaryon</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=War_for_the_White_Cloaks&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.4</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.5</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.6</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\">1.7</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_year_of_the_three_brides_-_49_ac.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\">1.8</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Year of the Three Brides - 49 AC.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403123434\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.037 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.059 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 906/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8929/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3536/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2061/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 3600/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.010/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 4.51 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   50.170      1 -total\n 59.28%   29.740      1 Template:Date\n 33.78%   16.949      9 Template:Ref\n 21.38%   10.724      9 Template:Ref/core\n  4.52%    2.270      1 Template:Quote\n  4.14%    2.079      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:25110-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403123434 and revision id 244614\n -->\n",
